quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  20,90,"wlqd qal harun libani 'iisrayiyl min qibal rjwe musaa 'ilyhm: ya qawm 'iinama akhtubrtm bhdha alejl; lyzhr almumin minkum min alkafr, wa'iina rabakum alrhmn la ghyrh fatabieuni fima 'adeukum 'iilayh min eibadat allh, wa'atieuu 'amri fi aitibae shreh"
  20,91,"qal eubbad aleijl mnhm: ln nazal muqimin ealaa eibadat aleijl hataa yarjie 'iilayna mwsa"
  20,92,"qal musaa li'akhih harwn: ay shay' manaeak hin ra'aytahum dllu ean dinahum 'an la ttbeny, ftlhq bi wttrkhm? 'afaeasayt 'amri fima 'amartuk bih min khlafty wal'iislah bedy?"
  20,93,"qal musaa li'akhih harwn: ay shay' manaeak hin ra'aytahum dllu ean dinahum 'an la ttbeny, ftlhq bi wttrkhm? 'afaeasayt 'amri fima 'amartuk bih min khlafty wal'iislah bedy?"
  20,94,"thm 'akhadh musaa blhyt harun wrash yjrruh 'ilyh, faqal lah harwn: ya abn amy la tamasuk bilihyati wala bsher rasy, 'iiniy khft - 'iina trkthm wlhqt bik - 'ana tqwl: frraqt bayn bani 'israyyl, walam tahfaz wsyty bihusn reaythm"
  20,95,"qal musaa llsamry: fama shank ya samry? wama aldhy deak 'iilaa ma felth?"
  20,96,"qal alsamry: ra'ayt ma lam yrwh - wahu jbryl ealayh alslam - ealaa frs, waqt khurujihim min albahr wghrq fireawn wjnwdh, fakhdht bkfy turabana min 'athar hafr frs jbryl, falqyth ealaa alhly aldhy sunieat minh alejl, fakan eijlana jsdana lah khwar; bala' wftnt, wkdhlk zyant li nafsi alammart bialsuw' hdha alsnye"
  20,97,"qal musaa llsamry: fadhhab fa'iina lak fi hyatk 'ana taeish mnbwdhana taqul likuli ahd: la 'amass wala 'umassu, wa'iina lak maweidana ledhabk weqabk, ln yukhlfk allah 'iyah, wasawf tlqah, wanzur 'iilaa mebwdk aldhy aqmt ealaa eibadatih lnuhrqnnah balnar, thuma lnudhrynnah fi alymm tdhryt"
  20,98,"'inma 'ilhkm - 'ayuha alnaas - hu allah aladhi la mebwd bihaqi 'iilaa hw, wasie ealamah kl shy'"
  20,99,"kma qasasna ealayk - 'ayuha alrasul - 'anba' musaa wafireawn wqwmhma, nkhbrk banba' alssabiqin lk. waqad ataynak min eindina hdha alquran dhikraa liman ytdhkr"
  20,100,"mn 'aerid ean hdha alqran, walam yusadiq bh, walam yaemal bima fyh, fa'iinah yati rabih yawm alqiamat yahmil 'ithmana ezymana"
  20,101,"khaldyn fi aledhab, wsa'hm dhlk alhml althaqil min alatham hayth awrdhm alnar"
  20,102,"ywm yanfukh almlak fi \"alqrn\" lsyht albeth, wanasuq alkafirin dhlkm alyawm wahum zrq, tghyart alwanhm weywnhm; min shdt al'ahdath walahwal"
  20,103,"ythamswn bynhm, yaqul bedhm lbed: ma labithtum fi alhayat aldunya 'iilaa eshrt ayam"
  20,104,nahn 'aelam bima yaqulun wyusirrun hyn yaqul aelmhm wawfahm eqla ma labithtum 'iilaa ywmana wahdana; lqisar mdt aldunya fi 'anfusihim yawm alqyamt